{"tid":927784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本平成年最後一屆美男選拔賽 冠軍風采竟被混入正妹蓋過","createTime":"2018-12-04T11:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T04:28:02.000Z","uid":9573,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"404e5cce80df01896b2d6bbcc5e6b7425307218a","tid":927784,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"日本《JUNON SUPER BOY》美男選拔賽是不少男星進入演藝圈的跳板，此次舉辦的比賽中，由出身於北海道的松本大輝奪冠，只不過更令人注意的是，怎麼會有正妹混入比賽？引發網友熱烈討論，關注度更壓過松本大輝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/02/1669277-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F02%2F1669277-XXL.jpg&h=dfaf9b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲今年的《JUNON SUPER BOY》是平成年的最後一屆。<br />\n<br />\n《JUNON SUPER BOY》孕育出不少超人氣男星，包括小池徹平、三浦翔平、菅田將輝等人，都是在美男選拔比賽中脫穎而出，現在在演藝圈發光發亮的一線男星。今年的比賽是日本「平成」年的最後一屆，更受到各界的關注，最後由北海道出身的19歲學生松本大輝勝出，身高有182公分的他，有著陽光爽朗的笑容，在鏡頭前秀出籃球炫技，獲得青睞奪下第一名，被外界看好將是下一個爆紅的菅田將輝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/02/1669275-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F02%2F1669275-XXL.jpg&h=339405b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲松本大輝獲得第一名。<br />\n<br />\n只不過在眾多參賽者中，卻有一名正妹更吸引人的注意力，渾圓的眼睛，配上鵝蛋的小臉，長相清秀可人，十分可愛，在舞台上靦靦的表現，讓人不禁直呼「卡哇伊」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/02/1669272-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F02%2F1669272-XXL.jpg&h=470cec3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼井手上漠外表超級可愛，讓不少女生自嘆不如。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/02/1669278-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F02%2F1669278-XXL.jpg&h=ad3b045a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但他不是女生，而是貨真價值的15歲男生，他是井手上漠出身於島根縣，身高163公分，據說他從小就喜歡把自己打扮成女孩子，雖然曾遭到排擠，受到異樣眼光看待，也難過、沮喪過，試著調整說話方式，剪短髮要混入男生堆，最後他選擇忠於做出自己，更勇敢參加比賽，完場前頂入愛華頓幫助球隊小勝1：0，令到高普興奮得衝入球場慶祝。雖然井手上漠最後只得到「自我品牌塑造獎」，但不只男生為他相當著迷，就連女生都自嘆不如，直呼真的好可愛，話題性也超過冠軍松本大輝，看來未來星途不可限量。"},{"pid":"42b65c5b24797fd6322c3cf67fbbbc61981df8f8","tid":927784,"uid":146558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:23:23.000Z","msg":"仲以為真係有女亂入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f41c711bf01fa26a932e61ecfdad98baf5e63b5","tid":927784,"uid":114762,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:25:50.000Z","msg":"更勇敢參加比賽，完場前頂入愛華頓幫助球隊小勝1：0，令到高普興奮得衝入球場慶祝。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7867baa364b52a672e67292e8ef32b3fb33f439","tid":927784,"uid":172616,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">最後他選擇忠於做出自己，更勇敢參加比賽，完場前頂入愛華頓幫助球隊小勝1：0，令到高普興奮得衝入球場慶祝。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b4b997922607a4ee62bf2c9ef3f22949bcee12","tid":927784,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5867bfb342f1458790b08e09014e3fadf0b30499","tid":927784,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"松本大輝個樣有幾分似我"},{"pid":"a98f226801cf6cf356a13319bbac10a816d155b6","tid":927784,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5757255cec49dfa52df50b7e665cc417e42ada80","tid":9277